  "texts": [
    "DiscussionArtificial intelligence-powered chatbots, such as ChatGPT and Google Bard, have been heralded as revolutionary turning points in the current AI revolution.",
    "These chatbots are LLMs that employ machine learning and natural language processing to interact with people via text or voice interfaces.",
    "The possible application of LLMs in medicine has garnered a lot of hype in recent months [2,26].",
    "Healthcare professionals may get evidence-based real-time advices from chatbots to enhance patient outcomes [27].",
    "For complicated medical situations, they may provide clinical recommendations, identify possible medication interactions, and recommend suitable courses of action [28]."
  ],
